{
  "stem": "12402.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one-- a week before-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] just a week before, a couple of weeks, so we had a-- a relative in a neighborhood town, maybe 10 kilometers away from us, by the name Ostrowiec, it was named.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- a brother of my aunt's came-- they were supposed to surround-- the rumor is they were going to surround the city of Ostrowiec so he wanted to-- so he came to our-- to our home to hide until the-- the thing will be over.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he'll go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he's begging my father should give him shoes, you know, we're going to have to run [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So on this-- this-- his name was Pinchas Applebaum, and he had a brother-in-law by the name [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they formed also a place for work, maybe five miles away from our town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was all bought off for money, you know, to make a place for work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then nobody worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just a name and they had a permit from the SS.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was all bought off for money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But how do they get their money?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they approach a lot of rich Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You want to-- you want to survive?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You give me $1,000.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It'll get in you in on the list.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a permit of-- You can finish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a permit for 500 people in this place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's called [INAUDIBLE], you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so this Pinchas, he was a relative, so he came to my father and he asked him for shoes, which did, my father-- he stayed maybe a few days until they took away-- they evacuated the-- the city where he was supposed to go back.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he went back with his brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
